A '''koozie''' (or '''coozie''') is a device, typically made of some type of insulating material, into which a beverage can or bottle can be inserted to retain its cold temperature.

A Koozie (sometimes pronounced "Cuzia")is a slang Eastern European term for encrusted nose mucus (or booger)>
